      <title>KKR以4亿美元的价格购买印度HCG的多数股份</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/kkr-set-to-buy-majority-stake-in-india-s-hcg-for-400-million</link>
      <description><![CDATA[KKR＆amp; Co Inc.将从CVC Capital Partners获得印度医疗保健全球企业有限公司的多数股份，价值4亿美元，使这家私募股权公司成为印度癌症护理连锁店的最大股东和唯一运营商。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-02-24/kkr-set-to-buy-majority-stake-in-india-s-hcg-for-400-million</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 24 Feb 2025 04:02:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
